WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:05.920
Hey, good morning, family. I'm excited to be with y'all today. I have a word

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:08.200
for you. I'm trying not to cry through the whole

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:17.600
thing. The Lord visited me last

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:35.167
night. Sorry, I'm going to get it together because I've got a message for you.

00:00:35.167 --> 00:00:39.800
Help me, Holy Spirit. Okay, all right, get it together

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:48.760
here. I had a visitation, an open-eyed vision that lasted for about an

00:00:48.760 --> 00:00:59.920
hour. The Lord showed me a lot of what's to come.

00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:03.600
God help

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:14.560
everyone. He told me to do two videos. He said, 'I want you to separate it and don't

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:23.160
do it all at once,'so I'll give you part one and part two. But I'm going to give you

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:32.640
the last of it first because it was holy. When Jesus

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:37.960
appeared, the first part was about the

00:01:37.960 --> 00:01:53.400
economy and what's coming financially for you people.

00:01:53.400 --> 00:02:01.080
And then the last of it was his heart—a cry for the lost. So I'm going to start with the vision.

00:02:01.080 --> 00:02:12.600
In this vision, I saw the sun going down, and the Spirit of the Lord said to me, 'Brandon,

00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:21.120
the sun is setting on this dispensation of time.'He said everything that humanity

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:28.520
has been, this part of it is coming to an end. The dispensation of grace is coming to an end, and they're

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:32.800
going into the tribulation. The tribulation is about

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:39.840
to begin. I saw the sun going down, right where it was getting ready to

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:47.280
set, and I could see the sun coming through the clouds. It was beautiful, but there

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:57.960
was no time; everything was timeless. It felt like there was no—you

00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:02.280
know when you feel your life is moving? But

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:05.600
it was just a total

00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:13.480
peace. I could see the beautiful colors coming through; everything was

00:03:13.480 --> 00:03:33.720
so

00:03:33.720 --> 00:03:40.080
beautiful. And then all of a sudden, Jesus stood

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:50.480
there. He had this beautiful robe on; I've never seen him wear it before in any visitation

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:59.840
that I've had. It had a white thread that was perfect right here, and it went

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:04.400
into another garment underneath it. He had a robe on top of it with

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:11.560
a hood that had white around the top. It was full of

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:20.200
different embroideries, colors like I've never seen before, like tapestry.

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:29.720
He had a huge wooden staff in his right hand, and it went from

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:34.680
the ground all the way up above his head. It was a very thick-looking

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:45.720
staff. His face had so much

00:04:45.720 --> 00:05:02.160
compassion. All of a sudden, I heard him say, 'One last

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:18.880
call. One last call. I'm calling my sheep. I'm coming. One last call.'It

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:24.520
sounded like a horn blowing throughout this valley. I looked upon this

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:33.000
valley, and there was a valley of sheep on a green pasture. Half of it was green, but half of it was

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:42.880
dark. All of these sheep that were the closest to him—because he was

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:50.520
upon a hill—were watching. The sun was setting; it was coming to an end. Everything we've ever known as humanity, from the beginning with Adam and Eve to where we are right now, he said the sun is setting on time. He

00:05:50.520 --> 00:05:56.480
yelled

00:05:56.480 --> 00:06:02.600
it:

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:13.840
'One last call!'All of a

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:20.640
sudden, down that valley, the sun started to shine upon the sheep. There were heavy sheep with big

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:26.520
fur, and there were skinny sheep that looked like they had been sheared and were completely bald.

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:32.920
They were grazing upon this grass, and all of a sudden,

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:42.520
they looked to him and started to run to the Father,

00:06:42.520 --> 00:06:49.400
and he was waiting for them. The heavy sheep were running—it was interesting because I could

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:55.480
see their legs at a trot, almost like a gallop

00:06:55.480 --> 00:07:02.880
trying to get to the Father. Some of the sheep were waddling because

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:09.320
they were heavier than others. Some sheep were barely moving, having

00:07:09.320 --> 00:07:12.960
a hard time, but they were on their

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:19.200
way. I could see the ones

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:29.800
behind; his face looked distressed.

00:07:29.800 --> 00:07:36.360
The Lord could see them, but they weren't

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:45.680
watching. They had gray fur and black on them. The sheep behind were

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:51.640
in the darkness, and they were eating, but they never heard him

00:07:51.640 --> 00:08:01.360
call. They weren't paying attention; they just kept eating. Time was running out, and

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:08.680
they didn't even know it. Those sheep were covered in soot, covered in

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:17.440
black, grazing upon the land. I just

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:21.520
kept watching his face as he looked to see if they were going

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:29.440
to hear him as he's calling because we're running out of time.

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:38.240
Humanity as we know it is coming to an end. Humanity as it's been for the last

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:44.320
6,000 years, before we go into the millennial reign, we're fixing to go into the

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:53.080
tribulation. That's what he was trying to tell everybody: that there was one last call, one

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:59.920
last harvest, one last push. I told you all this before—that the bells will ring in the church

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:07.040
one more time to sound the alarm of his coming. Now he's given me this; he came to me personally and

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:12.240
told me to tell you that there's one last call. If you're living on the edge and

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:17.920
not living for Jesus, is your boat ready? Are you ready for the coming

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:24.400
of the Lord? Is your heart ready for the coming of your King? If you're

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:29.360
riding the fence, you better get your heart right before him because you're about to miss the boat.

00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:40.800
The sun is setting, and people are asleep. Some

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:45.680
were awake and looking for the Lord. Those sheep were

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:50.200
attentive and heard his voice because the Bible says, 'My sheep will know my voice, and a

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:58.760
stranger's voice they'll not follow.'One last call. I saw that sun setting;

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:06.160
it went down, and all of a sudden—this is the end of the vision

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:12.240
with the Father. I've never seen this before in the spirit realm. I

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:19.200
could see the sun coming down and the light shined directly into

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:25.760
my spiritual eyes. I could not see anything else; it was just fire all over me.

00:10:25.760 --> 00:10:33.400
Then the sun set and went away. The vision instantaneously stopped, and the Lord started

00:10:33.400 --> 00:10:39.280
to tell me, 'I want you to tell my people that there's one more call, Brandon.

00:10:39.280 --> 00:10:46.600
There's one more call, and I'm coming. I'm giving them one more chance; I'm trying to get a

00:10:46.600 --> 00:10:53.400
great harvest of souls.'He was warning the people that he's coming. Pray

00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:59.240
over Israel and the things that he's showing me.

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:08.440
A great shaking is coming—more

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:16.600
than what anybody realizes. People are not prepared for what's

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:24.120
about to happen. The Lord said, 'Brandon, it's time; you have to get your boat ready even more.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:31.320
Separate yourself unto me.'He showed me people on YouTube

00:11:31.320 --> 00:11:36.520
that I have known. He said, 'Brandon, they'll be broke within a day; they're

00:11:36.520 --> 00:11:43.560
going to lose everything because their heart is not with me.'He said

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:48.560
every single one

00:11:48.560 --> 00:11:54.520
of them will be humbled; every single one of them will lose it that fast. Everything that they've

00:11:54.520 --> 00:11:59.360
ever had. Because, 'My heart is not that any man should perish, but

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:10.760
all come to repentance.'But sometimes we go through hard times because we're too stiff-necked. We

00:12:10.760 --> 00:12:16.800
are not listening, watching, or waiting. We're not keeping our lamps full or

00:12:16.800 --> 00:12:25.240
making him Lord over our lives. He's second, maybe third; you don't

00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:29.520
consult him at all. Sometimes you go to church, sometimes you don't; you don't really care.

00:12:29.520 --> 00:12:38.560
He's not Lord; he's not priority in your life.

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:46.880
There's going to be a great sifting of the sand, and you're going to see

00:12:46.880 --> 00:12:54.400
the good stuff rise to the top and the bad stuff go to the bottom. There's a

00:12:54.400 --> 00:13:02.600
line being drawn in the sand, and God is saying, 'Who is for me

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:07.440
and who is truly for me? Who is truly just riding the fence and who is truly against me?'Are

00:13:07.440 --> 00:13:12.400
you on the Lord's

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:24.000
side? If he calls one last call, do you hear his voice? Are you the one that he's calling that's

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:33.240
not listening? Is your head down in that grass thinking that you're safe? Do

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:39.560
you truly believe that if Jesus came back today in the Rapture of the church, you would go with him?

00:13:39.560 --> 00:13:50.120
Or is

00:13:50.120 --> 00:14:00.800
your relationship with God just convenient? I have to ask you these things. There's one last call. He's

00:14:00.800 --> 00:14:12.800
trying to tell you that he loves you. Do you hear him today? Don't turn him away. It's time for you

00:14:12.800 --> 00:14:21.040
to fall more in love with Jesus. It's time for you to give your heart and be sold out.

00:14:21.040 --> 00:14:32.640
None of the world and all of him. 'All to thee, my precious Lord,

00:14:32.640 --> 00:14:42.320
I surrender all.'Have you surrendered

00:14:42.320 --> 00:14:48.760
all? Are you riding the fence? Do you have one foot

00:14:48.760 --> 00:14:53.120
in the world and one foot with Jesus? Is it

00:14:53.120 --> 00:14:59.040
just a convenient relationship because you want fireproof insurance? The compassion of Jesus is

00:15:01.360 --> 00:15:06.560
much more than that. If you could truly see the compassion on his face

00:15:06.560 --> 00:15:15.080
that I saw for humanity—the concern that this dispensation of time is

00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:20.760
coming to an end—he wants not one man to perish, but all to come to

00:15:20.760 --> 00:15:29.160
repentance. Will you give him a chance today? Would you yield yourself over to him

00:15:29.160 --> 00:15:37.800
today? Would you tell him, 'I want you to be my Lord and personal Savior'? He's waiting with

00:15:37.800 --> 00:15:46.720
his arms wide open. Stop running. There are

00:15:46.720 --> 00:15:52.280
so many of you running, thinking, 'I'll yield over

00:15:52.280 --> 00:15:58.920
whenever I get older; I'll give my heart to Jesus whenever it's convenient;

00:15:59.800 --> 00:16:10.520
right now, I'm enjoying sin.'But the Lord told me to tell you

00:16:10.520 --> 00:16:18.040
time is over. Whether that is a year from now or five years, on the scale of

00:16:18.040 --> 00:16:29.080
eternity, it's nothing; life is a vapor. Hell is forever; Heaven is forever.

00:16:29.080 --> 00:16:36.000
Which one do you choose? If you die tonight in

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:42.800
your sleep, where will you spend eternity? You say, 'I said the sinner's prayer

00:16:42.800 --> 00:16:47.560
when I was a kid, but I live like the world.'The

00:16:47.560 --> 00:16:55.960
very thing you say you were saved from, you went back to. You

00:16:55.960 --> 00:17:01.040
got baptized when you were ten,

00:17:01.040 --> 00:17:12.000
but you haven't spoken to him since. Does he know you?

00:17:18.120 --> 00:17:23.120
People say, 'I know Brandon,'but they don't know me;

00:17:23.120 --> 00:17:29.800
they just see me on YouTube. You don't know me.

00:17:29.800 --> 00:17:36.280
The only people who really know me are my kids, my wife, my mom, and my dad.

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:51.400
You may have heard

00:17:51.400 --> 00:17:59.000
Bible stories, but that doesn't mean you know him. There's an intimacy

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:04.440
with the Father that is a day-to-day process. When he

00:18:04.440 --> 00:18:12.640
said, 'You prophesied in my name, you laid hands on

00:18:12.640 --> 00:18:19.680
the sick, and they recovered, you cast out devils in my name,'and he said, 'Depart from me,

00:18:19.680 --> 00:18:29.640
I never knew you.'Does he know you? To

00:18:29.640 --> 00:18:33.960
cast out a devil or lay hands on

00:18:33.960 --> 00:18:39.600
the sick takes

00:18:39.600 --> 00:18:42.840
faith,

00:18:42.840 --> 00:18:49.360
but do you know him?

00:18:49.360 --> 00:18:56.440
I'm asking you today to check your heart and

00:18:56.440 --> 00:19:03.840
cry out to Jesus and make him your Lord and Savior. Christianity is not always

00:19:03.840 --> 00:19:10.480
convenient; there's persecution.

00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:19.120
But I stand with him, and he visits me. He said, 'Brandon, the persecution

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:27.200
will increase, but the anointing will also increase.

00:19:27.200 --> 00:19:37.200
Do not fear man; fear me.'I do it for

00:19:37.200 --> 00:19:45.560
him because I want him to say, 'Well done, thou good and faithful servant; enter into my rest.'Every

00:19:45.560 --> 00:19:56.120
day I say, 'Father, use me for your glory.'For we have this treasure in earthen

00:19:56.120 --> 00:20:03.400
vessels that the excellency of the power will be known of him and not of me. That's

00:20:03.400 --> 00:20:09.280
all I have for you on this video, but I want to give you all a chance to ask Jesus Christ to be

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:17.840
your Lord and Savior. Say this prayer after me: 'Father, I'm a sinner. I've been away from

00:20:17.840 --> 00:20:22.680
you.

00:20:22.680 --> 00:20:29.520
I ask you to come into my life and make you my Lord

00:20:29.520 --> 00:20:38.880
and personal Savior. Forgive me and cleanse me from all unrighteousness.

00:20:38.880 --> 00:20:47.320
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life. I yield myself over to you; have your way

00:20:47.320 --> 00:20:58.600
in my life. You're the captain of my ship. I'm lost without you.

00:21:00.880 --> 00:21:07.240
Thank you, Lord, that Jesus died for me and rose again on

00:21:07.240 --> 00:21:11.480
the third day.'Believe it with your heart and

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:18.080
say out your mouth that he's your Lord. Then go find a Bible-believing

00:21:18.080 --> 00:21:24.720
church that prays, reads their Bible, and teaches you how to live by faith.

00:21:24.720 --> 00:21:34.320
It's that easy. Stop being a knucklehead; stop practicing sin.

00:21:34.320 --> 00:21:40.640
We fall down and skin our knees, but we do not do it habitually on purpose.

00:21:40.640 --> 00:21:46.480
When

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:54.800
we mess up, we run to God, not from him. Our sin is none of

00:21:54.800 --> 00:21:59.840
the devil's business, though he will tempt you and beat you over the head because

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:05.360
he is the accuser of the brethren. We have to get to a place where we say, 'Lord, have

00:22:05.360 --> 00:22:11.640
your way in me.'That's called

00:22:11.640 --> 00:22:16.200
grace. But there comes a point in time where people make a choice.

00:22:16.200 --> 00:22:21.400
You choose to live in sin, looking at

00:22:21.400 --> 00:22:28.760
bad things on the internet or choosing fornicating and

00:22:28.760 --> 00:22:34.000
adultery.

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:41.360
You can say no; submit yourself to God, resist the devil, and he will flee. Get yourself in

00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:47.920
the word, read the Bible, and pray. We're all a work in

00:22:47.920 --> 00:22:53.680
progress, walking our

00:22:53.680 --> 00:23:00.200
salvation out with fear and trembling. He will clean you

00:23:00.200 --> 00:23:05.840
up; it's a process. For those with

00:23:05.840 --> 00:23:11.640
addictions, don't give up; just

00:23:11.640 --> 00:23:19.920
keep going to him. When you fall, stand back up.

00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:25.680
I bless you in the name of

00:23:25.680 --> 00:23:32.800
Jesus. Thank you for watching. If this blessed you,

00:23:32.800 --> 00:23:41.480
like the video, share it, and comment below; it helps the algorithm. Persecution

00:23:41.480 --> 00:23:49.320
comes for the word's sake,

00:23:49.320 --> 00:23:54.560
but we just keep standing. Put a

00:23:54.560 --> 00:24:00.760
smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:24:00.760 --> 00:24:05.880
We will see you all in just a couple of minutes in the next video. Bye-bye.

